## Production and Filming

*West Country Men* is produced by [BBC Bristol](/BBC_Bristol), a production center known for its contribution to British television drama and comedy. The series is filmed on location in the West Country, with many scenes shot in and around the town of Chulmleigh. The show's production team has worked closely with local communities to ensure an authentic portrayal of the region and its inhabitants.

The series features a distinctive visual style that captures the beauty and diversity of the West Country landscape. The cinematography often highlights the stark contrasts between the rural and urban environments, emphasizing the unique character of the region.

